  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Woman who had their Second miscarriage before 12(th) week of gestation.The patient who
             is diagnosed as thrombophilia with recurrent pregnancy loss. Signed consent form.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. having experiencedsevere allergies, trauma history and/or operation history within 3
             months

          2. with a history of mental illness and/or family history of mental illness

          3. limb disabled

          4. taking medicine within one month

          5. suffering major events or having mood swings

          6. with a history of recurrent pregnancy loss

          7. having internal and surgical disease(after having variety of physical examination such
             as electrocardiogram/hepatic and renal function/blood routine and urine rotine)

          8. Chromosome aberrations in anyone of the couple.

          9. patients who have drug contraindications
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
